		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />The idea is that one's (possibly inflated) sense of one's skill will be tempered by the experience of trying to code the game on a platform where efficiency and memory usage restrictions are almost non-existent. To make a game of this type also requires level editor tools, which pretty much must be done on a PC.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


